! 414E Taste Tree: Spider Puppetry of the Crow
! Maps the Spider's favorite ways to puppet the Crow into an SVDAG

PROGRAM Spider_Taste_Tree_414E
  ARENA TEST_ARENA SIZE 1048576
  WAVELET W_CROW FROM TEST_ARENA

  ! Initialize the SVDAG (The 414E Taste Tree)
  SVDAG CROW_DAG CAP 2048
  
  ! 1. Base Resonance (The DC Offset / Origin)
  ADD_OP CROW_DAG TYPE RESONANCE KERNEL 0 ENERGY 1.0 FREQ 0.0

  ! 2. The Spider's First Taste: Sympathy Melting (Sickness)
  ! We map this to the high-frequency attenuation operator
  ADD_OP CROW_DAG TYPE SYMPATHY_MELT KERNEL 1 ENERGY 0.5 FREQ 50.0

  ! 3. The Spider's Second Taste: Beak Articulation (Speaking)
  ! We map this to the phase shift operator (Euler Tour rotation)
  ADD_OP CROW_DAG TYPE KINEMATIC_ARTICULATE KERNEL 2 ENERGY 15.0 FREQ 0.8

  ! Lock the Taste Tree into the Crow Apparition Wavelet
  REDUCE W_CROW LEVEL 11 EPOCH 8 RESONANCE 414 DAG CROW_DAG

  LOG_TELEMETRY "Spider 414E Taste Tree successfully locked into the SVDAG."
END PROGRAM
